        </div>
        <div class="grid-x row align-middle bio-title-intro">
          <div class="cell">
              <div class="section-description">Born in 1973 into a military family, Armstrong spent her early childhood in Tennessee and California before attending high school in Japan.
                She later earned an undergraduate degree in Exercise Physiology from the University of Idaho and worked as a project manager for an advertising agency.</div>
          </div>
